high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter.
Put the plate in the fridge then take it out.
Turn around and go to the shelf in the corner of the room.
Put the plate on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plate on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the edge of the kitchen island then turn right to face it
Pick up the round plate from the kitchen island
Turn right and walk around the kitchen island to the fridge
Put the plate into the fridge then remove it
Turn around and walk around to the dark wooden shelf in the opposite corner of the room
Put the plate on the middle shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the round plate on the wooden shelf

high_descs: turn right and walk to the left side of the kitchen island
grab a black plate off of the kitchen island counter top in front of you
turn right and walk to the end of the room, then turn left and walk to the end of the room where the fridge is, and turn right to face the fridge
place the plate inside of the fridge, let it cool, then take it back out
turn around and walk over to the stove at the end of the room, then turn left and walk to the end of the room with the brown shelves in the corner
place the plate on the middle brown shelf
anns.task_desc: place a cooled off black plate on the middle brown shelf in the corner of the room
